Pod::Strip - Remove POD from Perl code

Pod::Strip is a subclass of Pod::Simple that strips all POD from Perl Code.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Build.PL
    ./Build
    ./Build test
    ./Build install

